              "type": "stat_block_section"
            },
            "effect": "The tripkee makes a ranged Strike (with a +9 attack modifier) against a Medium or smaller creature within 20 feet. On a hit, the target is off-guard and takes a \u201310-foot circumstance penalty to its Speeds. On a critical hit, the creature is restrained instead. The DC to Escape the net is 16. A creature adjacent to the target can Interact with the net to remove it.",
